39void
40nvkm_fifo_pause(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo, unsigned long *flags)
41{
42 return fifo->func->pause(fifo, flags);
43}
44
45void
46nvkm_fifo_start(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo, unsigned long *flags)
47{
48 return fifo->func->start(fifo, flags);
49}
50
51void
52nvkm_fifo_chan_put(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo, unsigned long flags,
53 struct nvkm_fifo_chan **pchan)
54{
55 struct nvkm_fifo_chan *chan = *pchan;
56 if (likely(chan)) {
57 *pchan = NULL;
58 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->lock, flags);
59 }
60}
61
62struct nvkm_fifo_chan *
63nvkm_fifo_chan_inst(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo, u64 inst, unsigned long *rflags)
64{
65 struct nvkm_fifo_chan *chan;
66 unsigned long flags;
67 spin_lock_irqsave(&fifo->lock, flags);
68 list_for_each_entry(chan, &fifo->chan, head) {
69 if (chan->inst->addr == inst) {
70 list_del(&chan->head);
71 list_add(&chan->head, &fifo->chan);
72 *rflags = flags;
73 return chan;
74 }
75 }
76 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->lock, flags);
77 return NULL;
78}
79
80struct nvkm_fifo_chan *
81nvkm_fifo_chan_chid(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo, int chid, unsigned long *rflags)
82{
83 struct nvkm_fifo_chan *chan;
84 unsigned long flags;
85 spin_lock_irqsave(&fifo->lock, flags);
86 list_for_each_entry(chan, &fifo->chan, head) {
87 if (chan->chid == chid) {
88 list_del(&chan->head);
89 list_add(&chan->head, &fifo->chan);
90 *rflags = flags;
91 return chan;
92 }
93 }
94 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->lock, flags);
95 return NULL;
96}

98static int
99nvkm_fifo_event_ctor(struct nvkm_object *object, void *data, u32 size,
100 struct nvkm_notify *notify)
101{
102 if (size == 0) {
103 notify->size = 0;
104 notify->types = 1;
105 notify->index = 0;
106 return 0;
107 }
108 return -ENOSYS;
109}
110
111static const struct nvkm_event_func
112nvkm_fifo_event_func = {
113 .ctor = nvkm_fifo_event_ctor,
114};
115
116static void
117nvkm_fifo_uevent_fini(struct nvkm_event *event, int type, int index)
118{
119 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = container_of(event, typeof(*fifo), uevent);
120 fifo->func->uevent_fini(fifo);
121}
122
123static void
124nvkm_fifo_uevent_init(struct nvkm_event *event, int type, int index)
125{
126 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = container_of(event, typeof(*fifo), uevent);
127 fifo->func->uevent_init(fifo);
128}
129
130static int
131nvkm_fifo_uevent_ctor(struct nvkm_object *object, void *data, u32 size,
132 struct nvkm_notify *notify)
133{
134 union {
135 struct nvif_notify_uevent_req none;
136 } *req = data;
137 int ret;
138
139 if (nvif_unvers(req->none)) {
140 notify->size = sizeof(struct nvif_notify_uevent_rep);
141 notify->types = 1;
142 notify->index = 0;
143 }
144
145 return ret;
146}
147
148static const struct nvkm_event_func
149nvkm_fifo_uevent_func = {
150 .ctor = nvkm_fifo_uevent_ctor,
151 .init = nvkm_fifo_uevent_init,
152 .fini = nvkm_fifo_uevent_fini,
153};
154
155void
156nvkm_fifo_uevent(struct nvkm_fifo *fifo)
157{
158 struct nvif_notify_uevent_rep rep = {
159 };
160 nvkm_event_send(&fifo->uevent, 1, 0, &rep, sizeof(rep));
161}
162
163static int
164nvkm_fifo_class_new(struct nvkm_device *device,
165 const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass, void *data, u32 size,
166 struct nvkm_object **pobject)
167{
168 const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_oclass *sclass = oclass->engn;
169 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = nvkm_fifo(oclass->engine);
170 return sclass->ctor(fifo, oclass, data, size, pobject);
171}
172
173static const struct nvkm_device_oclass
174nvkm_fifo_class = {
175 .ctor = nvkm_fifo_class_new,
176};
177
178static int
179nvkm_fifo_class_get(struct nvkm_oclass *oclass, int index,
180 const struct nvkm_device_oclass **class)
181{
182 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = nvkm_fifo(oclass->engine);
183 const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_oclass *sclass;
184 int c = 0;
185
186 while ((sclass = fifo->func->chan[c])) {
187 if (c++ == index) {
188 oclass->base = sclass->base;
189 oclass->engn = sclass;
190 *class = &nvkm_fifo_class;
191 return 0;
192 }
193 }
194
195 return c;
196}

205static int
206nvkm_fifo_fini(struct nvkm_engine *engine, bool suspend)
207{
208 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = nvkm_fifo(engine);
209 if (fifo->func->fini)
210 fifo->func->fini(fifo);
211 return 0;
212}

223static int
224nvkm_fifo_init(struct nvkm_engine *engine)

226 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = nvkm_fifo(engine);
227 fifo->func->init(fifo);
228 return 0;
229}
230
231static void *
232nvkm_fifo_dtor(struct nvkm_engine *engine)
233{
234 struct nvkm_fifo *fifo = nvkm_fifo(engine);
235 void *data = fifo;
236 if (fifo->func->dtor)
237 data = fifo->func->dtor(fifo);
238 nvkm_event_fini(&fifo->cevent);
239 nvkm_event_fini(&fifo->uevent);
240 return data;
241}
242
243static const struct nvkm_engine_func
244nvkm_fifo = {
245 .dtor = nvkm_fifo_dtor,
246 .oneinit = nvkm_fifo_oneinit,
247 .init = nvkm_fifo_init,
248 .fini = nvkm_fifo_fini,
249 .intr = nvkm_fifo_intr,
250 .base.sclass = nvkm_fifo_class_get,
251};
252
253int
254nvkm_fifo_ctor(const struct nvkm_fifo_func *func, struct nvkm_device *device,
255 int index, int nr, struct nvkm_fifo *fifo)
256{
257 int ret;
258
259 fifo->func = func;
260 INIT_LIST_HEAD(&fifo->chan);
261 spin_lock_init(&fifo->lock);
262
263 if (WARN_ON(fifo->nr > NVKM_FIFO_CHID_NR))
264 fifo->nr = NVKM_FIFO_CHID_NR;
265 else
266 fifo->nr = nr;
267 bitmap_clear(fifo->mask, 0, fifo->nr);
268
269 ret = nvkm_engine_ctor(&nvkm_fifo, device, index, 0x00000100,
270 true, &fifo->engine);
271 if (ret)
272 return ret;
273
274 if (func->uevent_init) {
275 ret = nvkm_event_init(&nvkm_fifo_uevent_func, 1, 1,
276 &fifo->uevent);
277 if (ret)
278 return ret;
279 }
280
281 return nvkm_event_init(&nvkm_fifo_event_func, 1, 1, &fifo->cevent);
282}
